    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-black mb-1">About this estimator</h1>

    <p>Uncle Pong's Thailand Holiday Estimator is a free, browser-based tool that helps you build a realistic budget for a trip to Thailand — covering airfare, entry essentials, insurance, accommodation, food, transport, sundries, and going out, in your own currency alongside Thai baht.</p>

    <h2>Why we built it</h2>
    <p>Plenty of trips to Thailand go sideways not because of one big expense, but because of a hundred small ones nobody planned for: the airport transfer, the daily ride-hailing, the rounds, the late-night taxis. We wanted a tool that gives you an honest number up front — friendly, practical, and judgment-free — so the only surprises on your holiday are the good kind.</p>

    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p>You answer a short series of questions and adjust the sliders. The estimator applies research-based price ranges and a destination adjustment (Bangkok, Pattaya, Phuket, Chiang Mai, Khon Kaen, or multiple cities), then shows a live total and a category breakdown you can export or save. Everything runs in your browser; nothing you enter is sent to us.</p>

    <h2>About the numbers</h2>
    <p>Default figures are drawn from general research compiled in mid-2026 and are intended as planning ballparks, not quotations. Prices in Thailand shift with season, location, demand, and exchange rates, so always confirm current costs and entry requirements before you travel. See our <a href="terms.html">Terms &amp; Disclaimer</a> for the full picture.</p>

    <h2>Who's behind it</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 items-center sm:items-start">
      <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="unclePong.jpg" alt="Uncle Pong — your cheeky Thai uncle and host" class="w-40 h-52 rounded-2xl object-cover object-top shrink-0 ring-2 ring-aqua/60 shadow-lg" width="784" height="1168" />
      <p>The Service is operated by Genext Information Systems. "Uncle Pong" — the cheery fellow pictured here — is a fictional, good-natured host persona, your experienced Thai uncle, created to make budgeting a bit more fun. We are independent and not affiliated with any government body, airline, hotel, or venue.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Privacy first</h2>
    <p>There are no accounts, and your estimate is stored only on your own device — we never receive it. The site is free and supported by Adsterra advertising, which may set cookies; you can control this any time. Read more in our <a href="privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="cookies.html">Cookie Policy</a>, or manage what's stored on the <a href="cookie-settings.html">Cookie Settings</a> page.</p>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p>Feedback, price corrections, and questions are always welcome — reach us at <a href="mailto:support@thaiholidaybudget.com">support@thaiholidaybudget.com</a>.</p>

    <div class="mt-6">
      <a href="index.html" class="btn-cta inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-xl">Start your estimate →</a>
    </div>
  </div>


